headline.print_headline: Future of Subway Pitchman's Foundation Unclear After Raid
headline.main: Future of Subway Pitchman's Foundation Unclear After Raid

docs.lead_paragraph: Suspended Subway pitchman Jared Fogle's foundation, which encourages children to avoid the same obesity he experienced in college, faces an uncertain future following a raid at his home two months after the group's then-executive director was arrested on child pornography charges.

headline.print_headline: Police Investigating Ariana Grande's Video Doughnut Licking
headline.main: Police Investigating Ariana Grande's Video Doughnut Licking

docs.lead_paragraph: Police said Wednesday they were investigating video that appears to show Ariana Grande licking doughnuts at a shop in Southern California. Earlier, Grande apologized for saying "I hate America" in the same video.
